    <item>
      <title>匯豐銀行維持香港最優惠貸款利率於5.875%不變</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匯豐控股週四表示，在香港事實上的央行維持透過隔夜貼現窗口收取的基本利率不變，追隨聯準會維持利率穩定的決定後，該公司已將香港最優惠貸款利率維持在5.875%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-keeps-best-lending-rate-hong-kong-unchanged-5875-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:27:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>渣打銀行第一季獲利成長 5.5% 超出預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打銀行 (Standard Chartered PLC) 週四公佈，第一季稅前利潤增長 5.5%，超出預期，因利率上升提振了這家專注於新興市場的銀行的盈利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/standard-chartered-q1-profit-rises-55-beats-estimates-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:24:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港央行維持關鍵利率不變，追蹤聯準會舉措</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港金融管理局（金管局）週四將透過隔夜貼現窗口收取的基本利率維持在 5.75% 不變，以追隨聯準會維持利率穩定的舉措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-central-bank-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-tracks-fed-move-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 03:21:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前官員表示，日本的外匯幹預訊號顯示160日圓線已陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/japans-fx-intervention-signals-160-yen-line-sand-says-ex-official-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥倫比亞大學學者、前財政部長伊藤隆俊 (Takatoshi Ito) 週四對路透社表示，日本當局可能會幹預貨幣市場，以表明他們認為日圓兌美元匯率 160 是他們的底線。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/japans-fx-intervention-signals-160-yen-line-sand-says-ex-official-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 02:25:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日圓走軟，疑似幹預後大幅升幅回落</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-gives-up-ground-vs-dollar-following-surge-suspected-intervention-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日圓兌美元週四下跌，在隔夜突然飆升後逆轉方向，交易員和分析師很快就將其歸因於日本當局的干預。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-gives-up-ground-vs-dollar-following-surge-suspected-intervention-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 01:28:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美國補充戰略儲備前景推動油價反彈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-pick-up-prospect-us-replenishing-strategic-reserve-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油價週四上漲，從連續三天的下跌中反彈，因預期油價下跌可能會促使全球最大的原油消費國美國開始補充其戰略儲備，從而為油價提供底線。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-pick-up-prospect-us-replenishing-strategic-reserve-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 01:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韓國 4 月工廠活動萎縮，但對前景的樂觀情緒有所抬頭</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/skorea-factory-activity-shrinks-april-optimism-about-outlook-ticks-up-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週四的一項私部門調查顯示，韓國四月工廠活動再次萎縮，但隨著產量和訂單實現邊際增長，製造商的樂觀情緒攀升至近兩年來的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/skorea-factory-activity-shrinks-april-optimism-about-outlook-ticks-up-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 00:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜耳旗下孟山都公司在華盛頓法院贏得推翻價值 1.85 億美元 PCB 的判決</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/bayers-monsanto-wins-reversal-185-million-pcbs-verdict-washington-court-2024-05-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週三，華盛頓州一家上訴法院推翻了拜耳孟山都子公司因西雅圖地區一所學校化學污染而被判賠償 1.85 億美元的判決，這是該公司幾週以來第二次取得重大法律勝利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/bayers-monsanto-wins-reversal-185-million-pcbs-verdict-washington-court-2024-05-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 00:27:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
