      <title>日圓因疑似幹預而飆升，160被視為關鍵水平</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollaryen-extends-loss-amid-specter-boj-intervention-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週四亞洲早盤，日圓兌美元匯率飆升，交易員懷疑這是日本當局為阻止日圓大幅下滑而進行的另一輪幹預，160 水準被視為關鍵防線。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollaryen-extends-loss-amid-specter-boj-intervention-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:57:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通因貿易報告缺陷向美國監管機構支付 1 億美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-chase-pay-100-million-us-regulator-over-trade-reporting-gaps-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通週三在一份監管文件中披露，預計將與第三家美國監管機構達成一項決議，要求其因向監控平台報告不完整的交易數據而支付 1 億美元的民事罰款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-chase-pay-100-million-us-regulator-over-trade-reporting-gaps-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:40:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由於消費者支出仍然緊張，eBay 預測第二季度收入低於預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/ebay-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-expectations-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[電子商務公司 eBay 週三預測第二季營收低於華爾街預期，原因是收藏品和汽車零件等主要產品類別的需求降溫，導致其股價在盤後交易中下跌 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/ebay-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-expectations-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
